	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can have as many palette entries as you want, so in that sense, there is no limit in size other than storage space in the rom.  The palette that is loaded and used for rendering is only 32 bytes of which 8 are color 0.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


